Possible Features:
create and edit lists
categorize and sort list items
prompt reminders
assign "time to complete" attribute
detect and warn for time conflicts
calendar view
push back or cycle list items 
schedule recurring list items
social media shaming mechanism
alternative reminder outlets- email, phone, etc

Target Audience Characteristics:
tend to fail to plan ahead
looking to delay action or spend the most efficient amounts of time
various obligations for work or personal life
tech-savvy young professionals or students who don't use a calendar- but are glued to their phones

Selected Features:
create and edit time-sensitive lists of tasks
generate reminders for tasks / warnings of potential time management issues
give users visual feedback for the effect of "pushing back" tasks

App Definition Statement:
a scheduling app that helps make the most out of the time available to the overextended and the underachieving
